snippet: The S.&P. 500 and the Nasdaq end a sixth straight quarter of gains, a streak not seen in more than 14 years.
abstract: Stocks show little change, but Standard & Poor's 500-stock index and the Nasdaq end a sixth straight quarter of gains in streak not seen in more than 14 years.
lead_paragraph: The S.&P. 500 and the Nasdaq end a sixth straight quarter of gains, a streak not seen in more than 14 years.

headline.main: Wall Street Is Mixed, but Caps a 6th Quarter of Gains
